{"id":64149,"date":"2021-10-25T09:22:08","date_gmt":"2021-10-25T08:22:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=64149"},"modified":"2022-06-27T13:47:49","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T11:47:49","slug":"cotignac-france","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/cotignac-france\/","title":{"rendered":"Cotignac: The Cliffside Village of Provence, France"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Cotignac<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cotignac is a picture-perfect village dating back to Roman times that sits within <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/provence-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Provence<\/a> in the Var region. Despite its beauty, it&#x2019;s relatively unknown on the usual <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/french-riviera-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">South of France<\/a> tourist trail. This makes for peaceful streets and perfectly preserved nature that adds to its charm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134514\/cotignac-france-4.jpg\" alt=\"cotignac france provence village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"233\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cotignac france provence village\" class=\"wp-image-64630 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1324px) 100vw, 1324px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134514\/cotignac-france-4.jpg 1324w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134514\/cotignac-france-4-414x600.jpg 414w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134514\/cotignac-france-4-559x810.jpg 559w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134514\/co