beautiful squares with ancient fountains and flowers. As you go, glance up to the cliffs that tower above, watching the sunlight change the color of the stone throughout the day.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Cotignac is great to spend the night! <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/cotignac-all-accommodations\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all the accommodations in town.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6.jpg\" alt=\"cotignac france village church\"><\/noscript><img width=\"220\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cotignac france village church\" class=\"wp-image-64634 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1247px) 100vw, 1247px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6.jpg 1247w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-390x600.jpg 390w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-526x810.jpg 526w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-220x338.jpg 220w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-19x30.jpg 19w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-106x163.jpg 106w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-117x180.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-499x768.jpg 499w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-665x1024.jpg 665w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-701x1080.jpg 701w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-935x1440.jpg 935w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-300x462.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-600x924.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6-19x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134549\/cotignac-france-6.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-discover-cliff-houses-and-caves\">Discover Cliff Houses and Caves<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the unique things of all in Cotignac is the incredible cliffs that act as a backdrop to the pretty village. They are 400 meters wide and 80 meters tall! Within these cliffs are ancient caves, used by villagers for hundreds of years as shelter during times of epidemic, war, rebellion, or invasion. In fact, many of the houses are built into the rock itself and are still used as homes today.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"cliff houses cotignac france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cliff houses cotignac france\" class=\"wp-image-64753 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093716\/cotignac-france-17.