g 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08093727\/cotignac-france-18-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As you walk around, look up to the top of the huge cliffs that surround the village. Here, you&#x2019;ll discover the ancient watchtowers, &#x2018;<a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/DKcSJa9kUUrW7xSm9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Les Tours Sarrasines<\/a>&#x2019;. They date back to the 12th century, acting as a lookout point to protect the village and its people during times of invasion.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>How to visit the caves<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s possible to pay a small fee to enter the caves. Follow the signposts from behind the town hall to get there. Once you&#x2019;ve climbed the stairs within the cave, you&#x2019;ll reach a fantastic viewpoint above.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> there is also <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/sd1AqMiAiLGuL1Bd6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">another viewpoint<\/a> you can hike up to. This is an excellent spot to visit at sunset for views over the village and countryside below.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/64149&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08103834\/cotignac-france-pin-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08103834\/cotignac-france-pin-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08103834\/cotignac-france-pin-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Cotignac: The Cliffside Village of Provence, France\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-try-delicious-local-food-and-drink\">Try Delicious Local Food and Drink<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cotignac isn&#x2019;t just pretty to look at; its extraordinary natural landscape is also the perfect place to produce olive oil and wine. You can sample some of these products at the weekly Tuesday morning market, where you&#x2019;ll find fresh fruit, veggies, honey, olive oil, wines, and even clothing.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092025\/cotignac-france-11-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"cotignac restaurant\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cotignac restaurant\" class=\"wp-image-64741 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092025\/cotignac-france-11-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092025\/cotignac-france-11-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092025\/cotignac-france-11-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092025\/cotignac-france-11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092025\/cotignac-france-11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads