40x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The village has also become famous in recent years for its small microbrewery, La Tuf Craft Beer. Make sure to check out the brewery and sample some of the unique recipes and flavors. What&#x2019;s more, the brewery put on events every week, such as live music, DJ sets, and tournaments.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Did you know<\/strong>? The brewery is called La Tuf, as this is the name of the rock that makes up the Cotignac cliff.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/bordeaux\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bordeaux , the wine capital of France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3.jpg\" alt=\"cotignac france village provence\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cotignac france village provence\" class=\"wp-image-64628 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1425px) 100vw, 1425px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3.jpg 1425w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-445x600.jpg 445w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-601x810.jpg 601w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-570x768.jpg 570w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-760x1024.jpg 760w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-802x1080.jpg 802w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-1069x1440.jpg 1069w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-300x404.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-600x808.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134500\/cotignac-france-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-explore-the-nearby-waterfalls\">Explore the Nearby Waterfalls<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Sillans-la-Cascade<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Close to Cotignac (7 km), discover the magical falls of Sillans-la-Cascade, one of the most beautiful waterfalls in France! The turquoise blue pools and powerful waterfall lie on the edge of the Verdon natural park and are a must-see on your trip to Cotignac.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How to get there:<\/strong> Drive to the car park before starting a 15-minute walk through the dappled woodland. Please note that you are not allowed to swim in the pools. This restriction has been put in place to protect the rocks and nature in the area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7.jpg\" alt=\"cotignac france watrerfall Sillans-la-Cascade\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cotignac france watrerfall Sillans-la-Cascade\" class=\"wp-image-64636 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134602\/cotignac-france-7.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>Gorges du Verdon<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have time on your trip to Cotignac, it&#x2019;s worth taking a day trip to Gorges du Verdon, a 1.5-hour drive away. The gorge is one of the biggest in Europe and is one of the most amazing natural experiences in France. Hire a kayak and paddle along the turquoise blue water before reaching a beautiful waterfall.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Everything about:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/gorges-du-verdon\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gorges du Verdon in France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"gorge du verdon france canyon\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"gorge du verdon france canyon\" class=\"wp-image-64587 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-france-4-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/05144537\/gorge-du-verdon-fran