=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\">Best Time to Visit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Anytime between the months of May to October is a great time to visit Cotignac. It rarely gets busy because of its remote location, and the peak summer months can be a great time to enjoy the sunshine, hikes, nearby waterfalls, and kayaking.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/sarlat-dordogne\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Everything about the Dordogne Valley!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134425\/cotignac-france-1.jpg\" alt=\"cotignac france colorful street\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cotignac france colorful street\" class=\"wp-image-64624 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1395px) 100vw, 1395px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134425\/cotignac-france-1.jpg 1395w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134425\/cotignac-france-1-436x600.jpg 436w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134425\/cotignac-france-1-589x810.jpg 589w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134425\/cotignac-france-1-246x338.jpg 246w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06134425\/cotignac-france-1-22x30.jpg 22w,