et St&#xE9;phanie (Bakery)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"hotels\">Best Places to Stay in Cotignac<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are lots of beautiful places to stay in Cotignac, from Provencal villas and charming guesthouses to boutique hotels and even cave houses! For more options, look to stay in a bigger city like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/marseille\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Marseille<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/nice-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nice<\/a> and visit Cotignac on a day trip.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/cotignac-all-accommodations\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all hotels and apartments in town.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092002\/cotignac-france-9.jpg\" alt=\"best place to stay cotignac france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best place to stay cotignac france\" class=\"wp-image-64736 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092002\/cotignac-france-9.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092002\/cotignac-france-9-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/08092002\/c